Data Deletion Instructions
To request deletion of your personal data from our Fashion Followers application:

Email Request: Send an email to [your email address] with the subject line "Data Deletion Request - Fashion Followers"
Required Information: Please include the following information in your request:

Your full name
Your Instagram username (if applicable)
Date of your last interaction with our service
Brief description of the data you want deleted


Verification: We may need to verify your identity to process your request
Timeframe: We will process all deletion requests within 30 days of receipt and send you a confirmation email once completed
Data Scope: Upon request, we will delete all personal information associated with your account, including search history, preferences, and any stored fashion brand recommendations
Third-Party Data: Please note that while we will delete data from our systems, we cannot guarantee removal of your data from cached or archived versions of our site that may be saved by search engines or other third parties outside our control

If you have any questions about the data deletion process, please contact us at [your email address].
You can add this text to your privacy policy page or create a separate data deletion page. For Facebook's requirements, you'll need to provide the URL for this page in the "Data deletion instructions URL" field in your app settings.
